Prof.Hostovsky is a wonderful instructor. He makes the class interesting as a result I never like to miss his lectures. He uses an effective way of teaching unlike other profs.
A very effective professor, gives great examples of issues relating to the course. Unique style of teaching allowing us as a big class to individually participate in lectures.
